"{\"uid\": \"binnews.com-content-2024-07-31-simone-biles-claps-back-at-critics-of-her-hair-at-paris-olympics\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Photo:Getty Images  Simone Bilesis shutting down critics of her hair at the2024 Paris Olympics.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 95, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 80, \"end\": 94, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Paris Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"On Tuesday (July 30), Biles took to her Instagram Story to address negative comments about her hair, perPEOPLE.\", \"from\": 97, \"to\": 208, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 137, \"end\": 152, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Instagram Story\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The now eight-time Olympic gold medalist shared a video of herself using a handheld fan to cool off during a 45-minute bus ride with no air conditioning amid the Paris heatwave.\", \"from\": 210, \"to\": 387, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 372, \"end\": 377, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999936076498801, \"rank\": 6.3923910445503056e-06, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Do not come for me about my hair,\\\" Biles, who was sporting a ponytail, captioned the video.\", \"from\": 389, \"to\": 481, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"IT WAS DONE but bus has NO AC & it's like 9,000 degrees.\\\"\", \"from\": 482, \"to\": 540, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She later posted a photo reminding people that it's not okay to comment on 